### 2. 📄 .gitignore (Ignore These Files)

GitHub repo mein "Add file" → "Create new file" → **.gitignore**

```gitignore
# Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp.js

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.production

# Logs
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Data
data/
*.json
!package.json

# Uploads
uploads/
temp/
